    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is currently not suitable for daily driving without major mechanical attention. The engine struggles to idle and produces a noticeable tapping sound, likely requiring a top-end rebuild. The transmission shifts harshly between second and third gears, and there is significant rust along the rocker panels and rear wheel arches. Inside, the upholstery is heavily worn with several tears in the driver's seat. This is a project car for someone with the tools and time to restore it, or it could serve as a valuable source of parts.",
      "price": 3200.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle represents a distinguished opportunity for the discerning driver. Featuring a robust powertrain and a refined interior, the automobile has been preserved to a high standard, ensuring both reliability and prestige. Every component has been rigorously inspected to verify mechanical integrity and lasting aesthetic appeal. Experience a seamless fusion of performance and sophistication, offered now at an exceptional value.",
      "price": 34500.0,
