      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm looking for a new home for my reliable ride. It's been well-loved and is in really solid shape, making it perfect for someone who wants a dependable car without the brand-new price tag. It runs beautifully and has plenty of adventures left in it! If you're looking for a trustworthy vehicle that\u2019s ready to hit the road today, this is definitely the one for you. Come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 29900.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_16_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_16",
      "description": "This E92 M3 features the high-revving S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8, a masterpiece of engineering boasting eight individual throttle bodies and a 12.0:1 compression ratio. Power is delivered through a precise 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-differential lock, ensuring optimal traction out of apexes. The chassis remains composed thanks to Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and a carbon-fiber reinforced plastic (CFRP) roof panel that lowers the center of gravity. This example is mechanically robust with documented rod bearing and throttle actuator service, ensuring the valvetrain and VANOS system perform to factory specifications. While showing minor signs of road use consistent with its age, the drivetrain and suspension kinematics remain sharp and track-ready.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "2019 Sedan. Reliable performance. Clean interior. Regular maintenance performed. Minor exterior scratches. Title in hand.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_17_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_17",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle strikes the perfect balance between performance and comfort. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, accented only by minor, expected road wear that speaks to its honest history. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of well-preserved materials and fully functional electronics, reflecting a smoke-free and pet-free environment. Recent service records confirm a history of diligent care, ensuring the engine runs smoothly and the handling remains crisp. This car offers a premium driving experience, combining a polished appearance with the peace of mind that comes from a well-documented life on the road. It is a reliable, eye-catching companion ready for its next owner.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained vehicle that exemplifies performance and reliability. This unit has undergone a comprehensive multi-point inspection, ensuring all mechanical systems operate within optimal parameters. The exterior retains a professional finish, while the interior provides a refined driving environment. A premier choice for the discerning buyer seeking a balance of luxury and proven longevity.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, she's been a total joy to own. It's in really solid shape, super dependable, and has been well-loved and looked after. It runs like a dream and is ready for a new home! If you're looking for a great car that's ready to hit the road today, this is the one for you. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions\u2014I'd love to chat!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Offered is a driver-focused 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power up to an 8,000 RPM redline. This example is equipped with the desirable 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory variable M differential lock. Critical maintenance has been addressed, including a reinforced rear subframe and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul to ensure optimal cam timing. The chassis remains sharp with refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers, maintaining the communicative steering and balanced turn-in characteristic of the platform. While the exterior shows honest wear consistent with a well-loved enthusiast vehicle, the mechanical vitals are robust and track-ready.",
